  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>There's a rich buffet breakfast every morning with a ‘make your own’ waffle station and some hot options.</p>
<p><strong>The Flair Rooftop Restaurant &amp; Bar </strong>is located on the terrace with panoramic views across Rome. <span>Executive Chef Alessandro Caputo has created an amazing menu, using </span>delicious combinations of flavours inspired by Italian and European influences. Watch him and the team at work in the open kitchen cooking up a storm. They also have an has an extensive wine list, so be sure to ask for recommendations. Open Monday to Saturday from 7pm - 11pm</p>]]></cateringDescription>
