  <description><![CDATA[<p>SINA Bernini Bristol has a great location in central <a data-udi="umb://document/57bc5f34b7074843b7f19f3fc6cb7ac4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/57bc5f34b7074843b7f19f3fc6cb7ac4}" title="Rome">Rome</a> between Piazza Barberini, home to the Fontana di Tritone, and Via Veneto, one of the most affluent streets in the city. No two rooms are the same at this luxury hotel and its brand new Baroque-meets-Modern style will leave you in awe. Each room is decorated in its own unique way with rich colours, lavish fabrics and bold architectural features. The hotel's striking new look definitely makes this a memorable place to stay!</p>
<p>The Trevi Fountain, Colosseum, Vatican City and St Paul’s cathedral are all within a 20 minute walk. You'll also be able to hop on a bus or take a taxi from the rank just outside the hotel if you prefer. The hotel's roof terrace is a true treasure in Rome's historical centre, giving you a 360 degree view of the city. Relax up here whilst sipping an Aperol or Negroni from The Flair rooftop restaurant. The restaurant also serves an a la carte menu and has a fantastic wine list. There are fantastic spa facilities too including a whirlpool, sauna and hammam with treatments available (payable locally).</p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 1 hour by private car from Rome Fiumicino airport.</p>]]></description>
