  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Signature Superior Rooms</strong> are about 27<span>m² and have views over Barberini Palace. They sleep up to two people and have air conditioning, TV, minibar, free Wi-Fi, safe and hairdryer.</span></p>
<p><span><strong>Signature Deluxe Rooms </strong>are about 29m² with views over the historical Palazzo Barberini or the quiet Roman street of S. Nicola da Tolentino. These rooms sleep up to three people and have been renovated using warm tones, luxurious fabrics and custom made furniture. </span></p>
<p><span><strong>Signature Deluxe Piazza View Rooms</strong> are in a fantastic position overlooking Piazza Barberini. They sleep two people. </span></p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are 40<span>m², decorated in a classical style and have a bedroom with a living area. These rooms sleep up to three people. They are located on the first floor of the hotel in a quiet location overlooking the streets of Rome. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </span></p>
<p><strong>Suites</strong> are 50<span>m² with a separate bedroom and living room and views of Piazza Barberini and Fontana di Tritone. These rooms sleep up to three people and are available on request, please call to book. </span></p>
<p><span><strong>Double Rooms for Single Use</strong> are available on request, please call to book. </span></p>]]></roomsDescription>
